\c 19
\v 1 Пророчество о <a name="02301900100004" ll:"SDBH:מִצְרַיִם:000001:Names of Groups|Names of Locations" il:"NBGbs20140204-40;NBGbs20120205-82;tb010705951;Gizah_Pyramids;Goshen;Egyptian_temple">Египте</a>. – Вот, Господь <a name="02301900100010" ll:"SDBH:רכב:000000:Move">восседит</a> на <a name="02301900100014" ll:"SDBH:עָב:000000:Clouds" il:"Altocumulus_cloud;White_cloud_111">облаке</a> <a name="02301900100016" ll:"SDBH:קַל:000000:Agile">легком</a> и <a name="02301900100020">грядет</a> в <a name="02301900100022" ll:"SDBH:מִצְרַיִם:000001:Names of Groups|Names of Locations" il:"NBGbs20140204-40;NBGbs20120205-82;tb010705951;Gizah_Pyramids;Goshen;Egyptian_temple">Египет</a>. И <a name="02301900100026" ll:"SDBH:נוע:000004:Shake">потрясутся</a> от <a name="02301900100034">лица</a> Его <a name="02301900100028" ll:"SDBH:אֱלִיל:000000:Images|Cult Objects" il:"Realia:4.6b;adr1305227007;Bolen00590;Bolen00300;Bolen00301;Realia0101;Realia0102">идолы</a> <a name="02301900100030" ll:"SDBH:מִצְרַיִם:000001:Names of Groups|Names of Locations" il:"NBGbs20140204-40;NBGbs20120205-82;tb010705951;Gizah_Pyramids;Goshen;Egyptian_temple">Египетские</a>, и <a name="02301900100038" ll:"SDBH:לֵבָב:000001:Think">сердце</a> <a name="02301900100040" ll:"SDBH:מִצְרַיִם:000001:Names of Groups|Names of Locations" il:"NBGbs20140204-40;NBGbs20120205-82;tb010705951;Gizah_Pyramids;Goshen;Egyptian_temple">Египта</a> <a name="02301900100042" ll:"SDBH:מסס:000001:Afraid">растает</a> в нем.
\v 2 Я вооружу <a name="02301900200006" ll:"SDBH:מִצְרַיִם:000001:Names of Groups|Names of Locations" il:"NBGbs20140204-40;NBGbs20120205-82;tb010705951;Gizah_Pyramids;Goshen;Egyptian_temple">Египтян</a> против <a name="02301900200010" ll:"SDBH:מִצְרַיִם:000001:Names of Groups|Names of Locations" il:"NBGbs20140204-40;NBGbs20120205-82;tb010705951;Gizah_Pyramids;Goshen;Egyptian_temple">Египтян</a>; и <a name="02301900200014" ll:"SDBH:לחם:001001:Conflict">будут</a> сражаться <a name="02301900200016">брат</a> против <a name="02301900200020" ll:"SDBH:אָח:000005:Object Referents">брата</a> и <a name="02301900200024">друг</a> против друга, <a name="02301900200030" ll:"SDBH:עִיר:000000:Towns">город</a> с <a name="02301900200034" ll:"SDBH:עִיר:000000:Towns">городом</a>, <a name="02301900200036" ll:"SDBH:מַמְלָכָה:000001:Groups">царство</a> с <a name="02301900200040" ll:"SDBH:מַמְלָכָה:000001:Groups">царством</a>.
