\v 5 И <a name="02301900500004" ll:"SDBH:נשׁת:000000:Dry">истощатся</a> <a name="02301900500006" ll:"SDBH:מַיִם:000000:Liquids" il:"Water_drop_001">воды</a> в <a name="02301900500012" ll:"SDBH:יָם:000007:Names of Waterbodies" il:"NBGbs20120207-20;Bolen00591;Bolen00310;Bolen00311;Bolen00312">море</a> и <a name="02301900500016" ll:"SDBH:נָהָר:000007:Names of Waterbodies" il:"NBGbs20120207-20;Bolen00591;Bolen00310;Bolen00311;Bolen00312">река</a> <a name="02301900500018" ll:"SDBH:חרב:000000:Dry">иссякнет</a> и высохнет;
